- if upvote.upvotable.is_a? Comment
  - post = upvote.upvotable.post
  %strong
    = message.sender.nickname
    님이 내 댓글에 공감합니다.
  %br
    = link_to excerpt(upvote.upvotable.body, length: 100), post.specific
- else
  - post = upvote.upvotable
  %strong
    = message.sender.nickname
    님이 내 게시글을 공감합니다.
  %br
    = link_to upvote.upvotable.specific_desc_striped_tags, post.specific
